posts.body: Throw it back to nostalgic summer memories with our brand new menu! For a limited time only.
Made with real cinnamon and inspired by delicious warm churros, these new drinks taste like the happiest memories.
Say hello to the sensational return of Lavender - the newest addition to our permanent menu!

reviews_data.review_text: Denver location is basically a drive thru Caribou. Only wanted a gift card, so not a big deal. Usually stop while driving to N.Y., but location in Raphine, VA. has closed. Patiently waiting for new store in Huntersville, NC to open soon. No drive thru, but indoor / outdoor seating. Favorite drinks are iced mocha coffee or iced mocha shaken espresso. Have visited the one in Charlotte, N.C. as well, where they share a store front location. Drinks were excellent as usual. Yum!
reviews_data.owner_answer: We're glad to hear you enjoyed your visit. Come back soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Place is amazing. Much better than Starbucks!

reviews_data.review_text: The Denver location is sadly disappointing to hear that it only serves light roast coffee or decaffeinated style coffee in the morning hours. I used to travel all the way to Mooresville to get Caribou coffee (medium to dark roast) and I was so excited when the Denver location opened only to be disappointed. The staff are very friendly,  I just wish they offered a wider range of coffee roast options.
reviews_data.owner_answer: We are sorry to hear you didn't have a great experience at our store. We appreciate you bringing this to our attention.  Can you email us at customerrelations@cariboucoffee.com so we can follow up with you directly? Please provide your Caribou Perks account information if you're a member. Thank you!

reviews_data.review_text: The Ho Ho Mint Mocha is So good! Great service and the staff is so kind and helpful. Great experience.

reviews_data.review_text:
I was so excited to leave this place a review because the staff was so incredibly nice & helpful, but I wouldn’t feel right not saying anything or giving a 5 due to how I felt afterwards. My wife and I both ordered “Shakers” here, and they tasted amazing….but within 20 minutes we both didn’t feel right at all, not even a quarter way through the drink. An hour later we’re home and both ran to the toilet, the first of probably 6 visits later that day.

I’m sure this is a one-off as the place looked clean & the staff was awesome - but to the staff - definitely make sure to check the dates on your products & make sure the machines are clean so nobody else gets sick. We’re both young and were fine, but not everyone fares as well.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi Austin, thank you for letting us know about this. We're very sorry to hear about this disappointing visit in our store, and we'd like to get in touch with you to discuss this concern further. Can you email us at customerrelations@cariboucoffee.com so that we can follow up with you directly? Thank you!
